<emphasis id="A39FEACDFFB3BA1FB1B8F5DBB43FFD12" bold="true" box="[1450,1561,699,732]" pageId="15" pageNumber="634">Habitat.</emphasis>
Dry forest.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB3BA1FB1B8F587BACFFCCA" box="[1450,2281,743,772]" pageId="15" pageNumber="634" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph id="915436DFFFB3BA1FB1B8F587BACFFCCA" blockId="15.[1448,2653,699,969]" box="[1450,2281,743,772]" pageId="15" pageNumber="634">
<emphasis id="A39FEACDFFB3BA1FB1B8F587B496FCCA" bold="true" box="[1450,1712,743,772]" pageId="15" pageNumber="634">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
Wilson's Bonneted Bat is an insectivore.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB3BA1FB1B8F46EB539FCE5" box="[1450,1823,782,811]" pageId="15" pageNumber="634" type="breeding">
